6: Gah... My head won't stop pounding...
9:
Doing a bit of stargazing might
actually sober me up...
13:
Oh, not again! How many times is he
going to do this?!
16:
He said he was keeping other
adventurers company during the
holiday festivities...
20:
That's EXACTLY what he said during
the anniversary celebration as well!
27:
But hey, it's Nimbus. What can you
do?
31:
Huh? The hell am I?
The infirmary?
33:
Those two really don't know the
meaning of "let sleeping tigers lie."
What a pain...
35:
What the—what's that awful jingling
noise?
46: WHAT THE HELL AM I WEARING?!
50:
Alk! You mind telling me what this is
all about?!
58:
Just "oh" ain't gonna cut it! Explain
yourself—and don't even try denying
it, I know it was you!
80:
What am I, a tree?! Don't decorate
me! No more ornaments, all right?!
85:
Now, now, Nimbus. Remember it was
your own shameful behavior that
landed you in this position!
89:
All right, no more beating around
the bush—
92:
Nimbus the white-tailed reindeer,
won't you work for us tonight?
104:
Like how you promised you'd help us
around the house with chores and
whatever? Except you just went off
drinking the whole time.
106:
It's like that, but this time without the
slacking off! We've got the perfect
job lined up for you during the
holidays!
112:
F-fine. I'll do it, so just... calm the hell
down. You're scarin' me.
129:
Th-that's enough, Claudius! It would
be disrespectful to laugh at him any
further.
132:
Pfft, no way! Are you kidding me?
Look at him!
134:
But no, seriously... Are you supposed
to be a reindeer? Or Santa? It's like
you couldn't make up your mind!
Bwahaha!
139:
I don't even know what I'm
supposed to be! So shut your damn
mouth!
142:
GAH!
You no-good brats, get the hell
away from me! Hands off the tail!
145:
What are you two even doing here
anyway? You got time to waste
faffing about in Palpebra?
148:
Not at all. This IS work! Festivals like
this bring out all sorts of interesting
folks—the sort that we'd want to
keep an eye on, if you catch my drift.
151:
Buuut, I'd be lying if I said I wasn't
looking to party it up too! Heh.
157: Claw! The tree is very beautiful!
162:
Ooh! I'll go and give it a look-see
right away!
172:
Oh, just the usual.
That being said, Claudius has been
a bit apprehensive lately. He's likely
concerned about the former chief.
174:
Were we still in the midst of a
heated rebellion, I would hardly pay
this matter any heed... But the
revolution is over, and we must work
to maintain the peace.
176:
That will entail improving our
relations with the aforementioned
deposed chief... A time-consuming
affair, no doubt.
179:
What about that king of yours? The
chunky one?
182:
There's nothing to be said. I have no
love for the man.
185: Heh. It's easier that way, ain't it.
191:
You're gonna help me out. Then you,
me, and that chatty panther are
going out for a drink.
193:
And while we're at it, we're gonna
eat some proper food. You ever try
roasted salamander?
196:
How could I ever turn down an
invitation from Lord Whitetail himself?
199:
Yeah, yeah. Cut it with the
formalities. You were laughing
earlier too.
203:
My dear lady... Could I trouble you
for a moment of your time?
207:
Hey, you. Guild's offering new
Adventurer's Insurance. Need some?
Too bad, you're signing up. Don't
worry, there's no up-front fees.
